{"tid":742401,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好食荃灣金坊泰國餐廳","createTime":"2018-07-14T13:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T03:19:56.000Z","uid":61394,"like":68,"dislike":140,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"c1df146eecab51a7f9c9cf73cf7cd56c8e0894d7","tid":742401,"uid":61394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"今日同女朋友行荃灣入咗間泰國野食<br />\n諗住食飽就算啦 點知伏到訓係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先叫咗碟生蝦 <br />\n隻蝦都唔知放咗幾耐 一啲都唔新鮮 <br />\n食落口仲要唔凍嘅 啲冰係啱啱放落底<br />\n但都唔好凍都唔凍下呀  碟野放多陣隻蝦可以當熟食<br />\n<br />\n之後叫咗碟海南雞 <br />\n本身都冇咩期望 但啲飯一舊舊 <br />\n我食兩啖真係食唔落 連女友大食開 都搞唔掂<br />\n<br />\n最過份係個冬蔭功湯<br />\n同你個仆飲落去同罐頭羅宋湯一似味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇咁過份間野呀<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/213808_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F213808_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=968c9961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/213820_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F213820_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=22f60af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n收我成四百幾蚊 我想食飽個肚啫 <br />\n唔係咁開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35c5e97e6d87bed1609f2699fdb0a4a888e975e","tid":742401,"uid":16061,"like":16,"dislike":54,"score":-38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:43:17.000Z","msg":"人地開左咁撚多年 比你唱兩句就收皮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acc70f927185b97af734f12500045d105e39be3","tid":742401,"uid":61394,"like":15,"dislike":16,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d35c5e97e6d87bed1609f2699fdb0a4a888e975e","tid":742401,"uid":16061,"like":16,"dislike":54,"score":-38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:43:17.000Z","msg":"人地開左咁撚多年 比你唱兩句就收皮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"唔係想佢收皮 係希望大家唔好中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a99afa12f629cff30c2fcd82677a50eb1366740","tid":742401,"uid":28195,"like":115,"dislike":3,"score":112,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"「連女友大食開」&hellip;笑撚咗"},{"pid":"caff1a672b65966e064643cad9b52a4951e21eab","tid":742401,"uid":56299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:17:37.000Z","msg":"幫你推推"},{"pid":"579ae624752a9f44beea54d0ed1014844e94a57e","tid":742401,"uid":23951,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"唔係平又唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但成個場好多大枱客，係咪兩個人去食d野會難食d"},{"pid":"ab546df70034b367711b25614a4033d82fd76e4e","tid":742401,"uid":103794,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"呢間野出名咗之後就愈做愈差"},{"pid":"742676c98d3018f3af0478f36f1e2f7bcb22e47e","tid":742401,"uid":126326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:19:43.000Z","msg":"海南雞飯幾高質 不過一年冇食唔知有冇差左"},{"pid":"a019940354e5be40208dcecc54349e4786577c7f","tid":742401,"uid":51924,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:21:48.000Z","msg":"新都城果間難食過屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f059fa623d827ead653445d93bb605e452977a","tid":742401,"uid":51924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"742676c98d3018f3af0478f36f1e2f7bcb22e47e","tid":742401,"uid":126326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T14:19:43.000Z","msg":"海南雞飯幾高質 不過一年冇食唔知有冇差左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T1