rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又去攞元氣 峰壽司同 築地黑門比先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de3b24947eb37d678e9b55d3ad1b0f57535b642","tid":742401,"uid":66171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T21:06:19.000Z","msg":"救命 點解啲人咁撚無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dce5de0a3b95fb7f3e75c681f8fc4299f32abc4","tid":742401,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T21:06:26.000Z","msg":"食泰國野去九龍城啦"},{"pid":"20184555893f8ff849cf15f0d1a8958fe5c83c2e","tid":742401,"uid":160537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T21:32:46.000Z","msg":"食過幾次 幾次都唔好受到 啲侍應好撚串。真。"},{"pid":"d1777267620d7e91eb36bfa97f5b53c9784aa19b","tid":742401,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T22:07:27.000Z","msg":"好撚細碟，又唔好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87f0fb5f0d36b0273ea2d1186258d9fd6749c65","tid":742401,"uid":36690,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6c2a464cf8f532cfb759bd75d73860907000b835","tid":742401,"uid":66171,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4820133a46719871d0ec8c2212ab2e8b7d410bb8","tid":742401,"uid":36690,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e1edb96c8ba8b5c7e4a28b7784a653a6b1aac5c","tid":742401,"uid":22455,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T17:47:24.000Z","msg":"我食左幾年都仲係好鐘意食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n野食幾高質價錢又合理<br />\n打手死全家"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T17:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T21:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來平時ching想食就飛去秦國食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係不解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又去攞元氣 峰壽司同 築地黑門比先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T23:15:20.000Z","msg":"香港就九龍城啦，價錢合理又好食。相就唔post，廢事俾人話係打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cd7f19804a1866bcc6be0be631ca7ce08980f8","tid":742401,"uid":84095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T23:22:59.000Z","msg":"食到肚屙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n狗也不屌"},{"pid":"02afac9edaa6cda66652c31f21349e1f6d5424b8","tid":742401,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T23:36:08.000Z","msg":"結論<br />\n香港人排隊食雪藏雞"},{"pid":"471e04d4835b1b42e6fe3b3903302578ac88ce74","tid":742401,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1df146eecab51a7f9c9cf73cf7cd56c8e0894d7","tid":742401,"uid":61394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"今日同女朋友行荃灣入咗間泰國野食<br />\n諗住食飽就算啦 點知伏到訓係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先叫咗碟生蝦 <br />\n隻蝦都唔知放咗幾耐 一啲都唔新鮮 <br />\n食落口仲要唔凍嘅 啲冰係啱啱放落底<br />\n但都唔好凍都唔凍下呀  碟野放多陣隻蝦可以當熟食<br />\n<br />\n之後叫咗碟海南雞 <br />\n本身都冇咩期望 但啲飯一舊舊 <br />\n我食兩啖真係食唔落 連女友大食開 都搞唔掂<br />\n<br />\n最過份係個冬蔭功湯<br />\n同你個仆飲落去同罐頭羅宋湯一似味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇咁過份間野呀<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/213808_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F213808_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=968c9961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/213820_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F213820_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=22f60af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n收我成四百幾蚊 我想食飽個肚啫 <br />\n唔係咁開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T23:45:53.000Z","msg":"其實點判斷啲蝦新唔新鮮？<br />\n刺身蝦即剝係唔凍 凍係佢剝好再雪 所以冰鮮蝦以新鮮而言係差啲 如果室溫好有可能即出俾你 反而夠新鮮 只係無凍過唔夠爽身 口感差啲 冰係減慢生菌唔係要雪凍佢 可能你食慣要爽口先鍾意 但泰國好多都係室溫就食 始終東南亞無咁講究<br />\n 海南雞飯可能放耐先一舊舊 但睇相無乜嘢 <br />\n冬陰公有加蕃茄 只係應該重少少重矛同酸啲<br />\n出面好香濃係用醬開 真係煲嘅係淡淡哋 似蕃茄湯 但都要有酸辣<br />\n<br />\n利申未食過唔知情況"},{"pid":"5bb62b4bdd90e569a12a39b827289b16143d348f","tid":742401,"uid":61394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"471e04d4835b1b42e6fe3b3903302578ac88ce74","tid":742401,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c1df146eecab51a7f9c9cf73cf7cd56c8e0894d7","tid":742401,"uid":61394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"今日同女朋友行荃灣入咗間泰國野食<br />\n諗住食飽就算啦 點知伏到訓係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先叫咗碟生蝦 <br />\n隻蝦都唔知放咗幾耐 一啲都唔新鮮 <br />\n食落口仲要唔凍嘅 啲冰係啱啱放落底<br />\n但都唔好凍都唔凍下呀  碟野放多陣隻蝦可以當熟食<br />\n<br />\n之後叫咗碟海南雞 <br />\n本身都冇咩期望 但啲飯一舊舊 <br />\n我食兩啖真係食唔落 連女友大食開 都搞唔掂<br />\n<br />\n最過份係個冬蔭功湯<br />\n同你個仆飲落去同罐頭羅宋湯一似味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇咁過份間野呀<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/213808_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F213808_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=968c9961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/213820_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F213820_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=22f60af0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n收我成四百幾蚊 我想食飽個肚啫 <br />\n唔係咁開心呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"